#  Investor & Media Relations 

We discover and develop medicines to defeat neurodegeneration.

The science is breaking open and the time is right for an ambitious and rigorous effort to address Alzheimer’s disease, Parkinson’s disease, ALS and other neurodegenerative diseases. We are applying deep scientific and drug development expertise to discover effective molecular therapeutics and have engineered a proprietary technology to deliver biologic therapeutics to the brain.

With a team of experienced and passionately dedicated scientists and drug developers, we believe we can succeed in meaningfully improving the lives of patients and their families.

##  FAQs 

[WHERE IS DENALI INCORPORATED?](#0)

Denali Therapeutics Inc. was incorporated in Delaware in October 2013 

[WHERE IS DENALI’S CORPORATE HEADQUARTERS?](#1)

Denali is headquartered in South San Francisco, CA. 

[WHEN IS DENALI’S FISCAL YEAR-END?](#2)

Denali's fiscal year ends December 31st 

[WHO IS DENALI’S INDEPENDENT REGISTERED PUBLIC ACCOUNTING FIRM?](#3)

Ernst & Young LLP is Denali's independent registered public accounting firm

[ON WHICH EXCHANGE IS DENALI LISTED, WHAT IS THE TICKER SYMBOL, AND WHEN DID DENALI GO PUBLIC?](#4)

Denali is traded on the NASDAQ Global Select Stock Market under the ticker symbol "DNLI"

Denali initial public offering occurred on December 8, 2017

[WHAT IS THE CUSIP NUMBER FOR DENALI’S COMMON STOCK?](#5)

24823R 105

[WHO IS DENALI’S TRANSFER AGENT AND HOW DO I CONTACT THEM?](#6)

**Broadridge Financial Solutions**

5 Dakota Drive, Suite 300, Lake Success, NY 11042 +1 800 353 0103

<https://www.broadridge.com/contact>

[HOW CAN I GET A COPY OF YOUR ANNUAL REPORT OR OTHER PERIODIC REPORTS?](#7)

Electronic copies of our Annual Report and other periodic reports are available on this website. If you would like to request paper copies of the Annual Report or other periodic reports, send your request in writing to:

Denali Therapeutics Inc.

Attn: Corporate Secretary

151 Oyster Point Blvd

South San Francisco, CA 94080

[HOW DO I CONTACT DENALI WITH ADDITIONAL QUESTIONS OR INQUIRIES?](#8)

Please use the [Contact form](https://www.denalitherapeutics.com/contact) for additional questions or inquiries.
